Name: Gold Pouch
Description: A jingle known by just about anyone. This pouch is said to make the world go round, sought out by any person looking for business, goods, or even food.

Name: Goblin eye
Description: Utilized by witches for potions, doctors for medicine and surgeries, and top chefs for culinary cuisines, the goblin’s eye still serves a purpose even in death. To preserve, place in a glass of water.

Name: Crown of the High Orc
Description: What’s a king without their crown? This crown, although missing some jewels, still glimmers in the sunlight, radiating its authority for all to see
